title: FEB 02 2022 - POLICE CONTINUE TO THREATEN TRUCKERS AT BORDER
description:
The Canadian truckers have been given an ultimatum from the police for blocking the Canadian-U.S. border, however the Alberta towing companies have refused requests to remove trucks from the convoy. Meanwhile, leaked documents from the day before Kabul fell have exposed just how unprepared the Biden administration was to evacuate Afghan nationals, and the White House worries that Biden will get Covid because it would show that vaccines don’t work. 




Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
